data.description: Welcome to this stunning listing! From the moment you step inside, you're greeted by a charm that matches your own. In the kitchen you will have updated granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. A second living area, perfect for entertaining family and friends! Brand new shower in primary bedroom. In the backyard you have a covered patio deck, perfect for lounging and enjoying the great outdoors. An above ground pool that'll make you feel like you're on vacation at home! And if thats not enough, there is also a shed! This handy space is perfect for storing all your outdoor essentials! ****SELLERS DO HAVE AN ASSUMABLE LOAN**** Don't miss out on this perfect place to call home!
